Table__Delete__ActionRow: (state, extData, errors, event, rowData) => { (async function() {    const { data } = await extData.__?.httpClient?.deleteMethod(`authentication/User/Delete?id=${rowData.Id}`);    })(); }
Search: (state, extData, errors, event) => { delete state.Table; extData.__?.setValueForm('Table', state); }
DialogAdd__BeforeOpenDialog: (state, extData, errors, event, tempState) => { return async function() {   const formRes = await formHelper.getFormByCode('Admin_User_Add');     return {formDef: formRes }    }; }
DialogUpdate__BeforeOpenDialog: (state, extData, errors, event, tempState) => { return async function() { const { data } = await extData.__?.httpClient?.getMethod(`authentication/User/GetById?id=${tempState.Id}`);  const formRes = await formHelper.getFormByCode('Admin_User_Update', true, data); return {formDef: formRes, initState: data } }; }
